description:
Steve Wohlberg was raised in a Jewish home in the Hollywood Hills, yet his family never prayed or read the Scriptures—even one time. In his teen years, he took a dark turn into drugs, alcohol, and wild living. At age 20, while heading downhill fast, Steve read a book about the life of Jesus. He has never been the same since!
